Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:35.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該放棄什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該決定什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:39.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}我算什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}早已經決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}有沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}對著神質問
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:49.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我並非獨自一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:58.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你一直在身邊 對我伸出這雙手
